      <h3>Zapier - Best for Beginners and App Variety</h3>
      <p><strong>Why I like it:</strong> With over 5,000 app integrations, Zapier connects almost anything. The interface is incredibly intuitive - perfect for quick automations.</p>
      <p><strong>Limitations:</strong> Can get expensive quickly at scale, and complex logic requires workarounds or Zapier Paths (higher tier).</p>
